    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know, i know. \"people care.\" i just don't see it. everything feels so automated. i'm just a username in a chat or a name on a payroll. if i just... faded out, it feels like the world would just keep humming right along without even a glitch. like im just a ghost in the machine. does that even make sense? that it's almost easier to just be nothing?",
